text: Fauscoum (), also known as Kilclooney Mountain, is a mountain in County Waterford, Ireland. It is the highest mountain of the Comeragh Mountain Range and the second highest mountain in County Waterford after Knockmealdown. ==See also== *Lists of mountains in Ireland *List of mountains of the British Isles by height *List of P600 mountains in the British Isles *List of Marilyns in the British Isles *List of Hewitt mountains in England, Wales and Ireland == References == * * "Fauscoum".
